caller_intent: The caller (Hector's daughter) is inquiring about the status of insurance documents that were supposedly sent to her.
resolution_steps: Agent (Gary) acknowledges the inquiry and requests time to check the status.
Agent commits to following up with the caller after verifying the information.
knowledge_required: Understanding how to check the status of client documents (e.g., policies, forms) in the agency's system.
Ability to schedule a follow-up communication with the client.
summary: Hector's daughter asked if insurance documents had been sent. Gary explained he needed to check and promised to follow up. The call concluded with a commitment to resolve the inquiry later.
